cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the category of "Computation and Language" (cs.CL) as it deals with speech recognition and language generation. It may also belong to "Sound" (cs.SD) as it involves processing audio data. "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) is another possible category as the paper discusses training models using weakly supervised learning. "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) and "Social and Information Networks" (cs.SI) are also possible categories as the paper uses social media videos as training data.
